{"tid":2250451,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"法國高速列車TGV團隊打造史上最美區間車本周抵台","createTime":"2020-10-20T06:04:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T12:54:51.000Z","uid":253829,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"90e7facfd3ff620cb313339286ea7bf69201f5bf","tid":2250451,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T06:04:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201020/BLVBK5MM4FFQRJA7RCZKWPOS3I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201020%2FBLVBK5MM4FFQRJA7RCZKWPOS3I%2F&d=h9s%2FmsO%2BhBO0acKdDJaYEXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=4dd3b3ff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201020%2FBLVBK5MM4FFQRJA7RCZKWPOS3I%2F&h=4878882a\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201020/BLVBK5MM4FFQRJA7RCZKWPOS3I/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/2HByxf4XGfn32pzioRsjoCtHxsU=/760x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ST3TXSS7JXL3LV6SWK6WWP3GIU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2HByxf4XGfn32pzioRsjoCtHxsU%3D%2F760x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FST3TXSS7JXL3LV6SWK6WWP3GIU.jpg&h=fa51f71f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由法國高速列車TGV團隊打造、被讚為台鐵「史上最美通勤列車」900型電聯車，首批2列20輛將於10月24日抵台，隔天開始測試，最快11月底上線試車，目標明(2021)年農曆春節前載客上路，但近傳出最美區間車恐成「憋尿列車」，因為10節車廂僅配置3間廁所，若有故障，乘客就得憋尿排隊搶廁所；台鐵表示，該車功能為通勤，設計以放大運能為考量，少1個廁所可提升40%運能。<br />\n<br />\n台鐵全新採購EMU900型通勤電聯車，採用一列10輛編組配置，共斥資253億元採購52列、520輛900型通勤電聯車，是台鐵編組最長區間車，首批2列共20輛今(2020)年10月24日抵台交車，透過船運自韓國抵花蓮港並吊掛卸船，並將從花蓮港臨時軌行駛至花蓮車站「展示」，隔天10月25日開始進行車子性能測試，最快11月底在路線上試車，民眾有機會看到最美區間車在西部苗栗和花蓮玉里路段飆駛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/I-pz1jNa2d4gaCIdKtnozTifuvM=/760x475/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HSJ7GA5EK6EGF3OIGBVTLHIL5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI-pz1jNa2d4gaCIdKtnozTifuvM%3D%2F760x475%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHSJ7GA5EK6EGF3OIGBVTLHIL5U.jpg&h=8f9bb0b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/XgBYi8Cc-l0Krz4Bx7nb1jZap3o=/2920x2085/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/WFBJBIPFQNFUBETO6VHJUCSXM4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXgBYi8Cc-l0Krz4Bx7nb1jZap3o%3D%2F2920x2085%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FWFBJBIPFQNFUBETO6VHJUCSXM4.jpg&h=f69feae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/3mmetVYL279FZjNWJvPWQkf039U=/760x542/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JDXWZQSPCFERZIJ2TTKNBP2K3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3mmetVYL279FZjNWJvPWQkf039U%3D%2F760x542%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJDXWZQSPCFERZIJ2TTKNBP2K3U.jpg&h=288e39d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/ta_e3l8KdE1lnDXXU3piFNCaHns=/3024x2160/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNH2CESKTFCBFMQHAX5MG6IN2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fta_e3l8KdE1lnDXXU3piFNCaHns%3D%2F3024x2160%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNH2CESKTFCBFMQHAX5MG6IN2A.jpg&h=d7b83ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/CAkfN68NlO1clsYywyhypvu9TY8=/3024x2160/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DMGUI3QW2JGHNI5XJU